The MEC for Human Settlements and Public Works in KwaZulu-Natal, Neliswa Peggy Nkonyeni will table the budget vote for Human  Settlements for the 2020/2021 financial year. DURBAN - The MEC for Human Settlements and Public Works in KwaZulu-Natal, Neliswa Peggy Nkonyeni will table the budget vote for Human Settlements for the 2020/2021 financial year. On Tuesday, KZN Premier Sihle Zikalala delivered the premier's budget policy speech at the Provincial Legislature.